set.seed(42)

Parametric bootstrap

Ordinary Least Squares

  pb <- PBootVAROLS(
    data = dat_p2,
    p = 2,
    B = 5000L,
    burn_in = 20

Lasso Regularization 

system.time(
  pb <- PBootVARLasso(
    data = dat_p2,
    p = 2,
    B = 5000L,
    burn_in = 20,
    n_lambdas = 100,
    crit = "ebic",
    max_iter = 1000,
    tol = 1e-5
  )
)
